title: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: The JarExporter is causing the application to go out of sync.
OB: When using the JarExporter to export a jar file, the exported jar file includes itself, which causes the application to go out of sync.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to prevent the application from going out of sync.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Use the JarExporter to export a jar file
2. Verify that the exported jar file includes itself and the application goes out of sync
